Customer ratings by feature

Additional details

Thera Care Gel Eye Mask Soothing Cold Therapy gel eye mask with strap and detailed English/Spanish instructions and warnings

Important information

Indications

Alleviates migraine, allergy and sinus discomfort; Minimizes eye puffiness and dark circles; Relieves eye fatigue

Directions

The Thera|Care Gel Eye Mask should be used as a cold therapy eye mask, applied directly to the skin with an adjustable strap for a secure fit. The pack holds its therapeutic temperature for a full 20 minutes. It is reusable and hand washable. Use only as directed and for external use only.

About Veridian Healthcare

Veridian Healthcare has a strong history in the Health and Wellness industry. Fresh on the heels of their past successful beginning and running Mabis DMI Healthcare, Steve Bisulca and Mike Mazza founded Veridian Healthcare as a return to their customer-centric business focus. It’s no wonder that Veridian Healthcare has hit the industry by storm, launching many, innovative, and unique products since its inception in 2009.

  • Hawaii
    4.0 out of 5 starsAmazon Vine Customer Review of Free Product
    Cheap, Works
    Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2024
    The Thera Care Gel Eye Mask is made of clear plastic and contains an aqua-colored gel. The mask has tiny eye holes that you can see through if you don't wrap the mask before use in a towel. The instructions that come with the mask say to not apply directly to the... See more
    The Thera Care Gel Eye Mask is made of clear plastic and contains an aqua-colored gel. The mask has tiny eye holes that you can see through if you don't wrap the mask before use in a towel. The instructions that come with the mask say to not apply directly to the skin, but the web page description says "direct to skin application". Just place the mask in the freezer for 1-2 hours, and it's cold, but does not become rigid. The velcro straps are a bit on rough side, and probably best used by those with lots of hair for comfort reasons. This is an economy mask at a reasonable price of $10.25. It gave me a headache when used without a towel, so I'd recommend using a towel. Recommended for occasional use only; if for regular use, I'd spend a bit more for a higher quality product.
    Helpful
